Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.44,0:00:04.57,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kageyama Shigeo, also known as Mob.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.57,0:00:06.40,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}A second-year in middle school.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.49,0:00:12.74,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}The second year of middle school kicks off\Nthe most sensitive period in one's life.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.74,0:00:16.29,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}People call it adolescence.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.87,0:00:18.87,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}Some hone their bodies playing sports,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.87,0:00:21.13,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}some work hard on their studies,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.13,0:00:23.59,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}some devote themselves to their hobbies,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.84,0:00:25.92,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}some polish their talents,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.21,0:00:28.17,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}some rebel,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.93,0:00:31.30,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}and some fall for the opposite sex
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.30,0:00:34.47,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}and get a taste of bittersweet love.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.97,0:00:39.94,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}All those youthful desires come together to\Nform the combination that is adolescence.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.35,0:00:47.32,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}And Mob was spending that precious time working \Nas an assistant at a psychic business for 300 yen an hour.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.82,0:00:50.53,Default,Char,0,0,0,,The reason is porn sites!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.32,0:00:50.53,Alt,Char,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.86,0:00:53.07,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Porn sites...?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.07,0:00:53.78,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.78,0:01:00.08,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}The curse that is on your shoulder \Nis a terrible one-click curse!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.51,0:02:38.89,Default,Char,0,0,0,,A-A one-click curse from porn sites?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.89,0:02:44.64,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}They use illegal adult sites to curse \Nyour shoulder and make you pay fees.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.64,0:02:47.65,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Curses nowadays are becoming digital, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.65,0:02:51.28,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Who the hell would believe that bullshit?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.73,0:02:54.90,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Just don't move for a second. \NI'll lift the curse now.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.41,Default,Char,0,0,0,,No, it's fine!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.20,0:02:59.53,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Your right shoulder is stiff—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.49,Default,Char,0,0,0,,The curse is strong.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.49,0:03:05.04,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Hey! I'm not paying for this. Sto—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.21,0:03:10.67,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}H-Huh? It actually feels good?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.67,0:03:14.42,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Sorcery Crush!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.59,0:03:16.22,Default,Char,0,0,0,,It's finished!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.22,0:03:21.76,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}Reigen's special move where he relieves the stress from physical fatigue
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.76,0:03:24.48,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}and gets rid of stiff shoulders and back pain.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.27,0:03:31.94,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I believe that I was able to lift the curse, but do your shoulders still feel heavy?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.94,0:03:35.74,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}I'm sorry that I doubted you. \NI feel much better!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.74,0:03:37.45,Default,Char,0,0,0,,May I come again?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.16,0:03:39.78,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.12,0:03:44.45,Default,Char,0,0,0,,So the 40-minute massage course fee comes to 3,800 yen.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.45,0:03:48.25,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}You idiot! Don't call it the massage! \NCall it the curse-dispelling!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.59,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Your change is 200 yen.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.92,0:03:53.09,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Here. You'll eat some won't you, Mob?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.09,0:03:55.92,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Oh, sure. I'll have some.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.72,0:04:00.34,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Master Reigen, you're getting \Nmuch better at massages.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.76,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Well, yeah. I've been trying \Nvarious methods to improve,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.76,0:04:04.81,Default,Char,0,0,0,,like reading books on Seitai and stuff.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.64,0:04:08.31,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Of course, it's only effective \Nbecause of spiritual power.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.10,0:04:10.98,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.73,0:04:12.90,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Such a waste!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.11,0:04:18.70,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Master, I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.70,0:04:20.87,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Well, this is rare.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.87,0:04:22.28,Default,Char,0,0,0,,You never start a conversation.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.70,0:04:27.00,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Well, I can use a little ESP \Nand I'm different from other people,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.00,0:04:31.13,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}so I came to discuss that with you \Nand ended up becoming your disciple.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.13,0:04:35.88,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}At the time, I didn't have anyone else \Nto talk to, so I'm grateful,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.34,0:04:39.38,Default,Char,0,0,0,,because you teach me various things and pay me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:40.30,0:04:44.10,Default,Char,0,0,0,,However, is this really okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.56,0:04:47.48,Default,Char,0,0,0,,That's what I've been thinking lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.94,0:04:53.56,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}Does he think his pay is too little? \NOr did he finally find me out?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.48,0:04:55.69,Default,Char,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.07,0:04:57.90,Default,Char,0,0,0,,How do I put this...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.90,0:05:00.53,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Rather than spending my time working after school,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.53,0:05:02.32,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that there might be
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.32,0:05:05.16,Default,Char,0,0,0,,some other things that I can only experience now...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.16,0:05:06.16,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.08,0:05:09.87,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Oh, so that's it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.87,0:05:11.83,Default,Char,0,0,0,,That is puberty, Mob.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.29,0:05:14.84,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Is there something \Nthat you want to do right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.84,0:05:15.96,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Be in a band?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.96,0:05:17.21,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Dance?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.63,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Hitchhike?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.63,0:05:21.05,Default,Char,0,0,0,,No, I don't have anything particular in mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.68,0:05:23.30,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Listen, Mob.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.30,0:05:26.81,Default,Char,0,0,0,,There's no need to rush into things.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.81,0:05:29.81,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}In my expert opinion, I'd say the \Ngoing-home club is the absolute best.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.81,0:05:33.52,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}You're just goofing off during \Nthe period you can goof off the most,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.31,Default,Char,0,0,0,,and that makes you a winner in my book.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.73,0:05:39.49,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Keep on lazing around \Nand make money from me. Got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.99,0:05:43.07,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Wait a sec, Takenaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.07,0:05:46.08,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I get treated like a weirdo just for being in this club!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.08,0:05:47.08,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Just wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.08,0:05:48.33,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I can't do it anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.45,0:05:52.04,Default,Char,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.04,0:05:54.75,Default,Char,0,0,0,,A club needs five or more members, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.75,0:05:57.04,Default,Char,0,0,0,,What should we do, President?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.30,0:05:59.13,Default,Char,0,0,0,,What else can we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.13,0:06:02.47,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}We have to find new members \Nlike our lives depend on it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.47,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Maybe Takenaka came back.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.47,0:06:10.47,Default,Char,0,0,0,,That's gotta be it! Takenaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.44,0:06:15.73,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}I just received a submission of resignation \Nfrom this club, so be forewarned...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.73,0:06:16.86,Default,Char,0,0,0,,The...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.86,0:06:18.23,Default,Char,0,0,0,,The student council!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.77,0:06:20.53,Default,Char,0,0,0,,This club will now be abolished.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.53,0:06:21.99,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Abolished?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.99,0:06:22.74,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Already?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.20,0:06:26.07,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Sadly, I'm going to have to ask you\Nto gather all of your things.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.49,0:06:30.45,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I actually just had a brand-new club request a room.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.45,0:06:33.04,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Q-Quit jumping the gun!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.04,0:06:35.46,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I'm not going to let you abolish the Telepathy Club!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.71,0:06:37.88,Default,Char,0,0,0,,The Telepathy Club bond is strong.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.92,Default,Char,0,0,0,,The student council's got nothing on us!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.92,0:06:42.84,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}You think you're all high-and-mighty \Nbecause of how you part your hair?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.84,0:06:46.30,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Shut up. Do you really want me to get angry?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.18,0:06:51.10,Default,Char,0,0,0,,If you're that desperate to keep this club going,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.10,0:06:55.19,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}bring me a new club member by\Nthe end of the school day on Friday.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.69,0:06:58.36,Default,Char,0,0,0,,F-Friday?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.69,0:07:00.61,Default,Char,0,0,0,,That only gives us two days.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.61,0:07:02.15,Default,Char,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.36,0:07:04.78,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Quit whining!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.78,0:07:07.87,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}If we ask everyone we see to join, \Nwe'll be able to snag at least one!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.87,0:07:09.49,Default,Char,0,0,0,,No, that's impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.74,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Recruiting season ended a long time ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.74,0:07:13.79,Default,Char,0,0,0,,No! I'm going to do this!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.79,0:07:18.25,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}We have overcome so many obstacles \Nup until now, haven't we?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.34,0:07:20.75,Default,Char,0,0,0,,President...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.34,0:07:23.92,Default,Char,0,0,0,,We haven't done a single thing...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.10,0:07:31.68,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Telepathy Club? Sorry, what the hell is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.68,0:07:33.18,Default,Char,0,0,0,,It's creepy, so no.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.43,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I've got a job.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.43,0:07:36.73,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Abolished? What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.73,0:07:39.11,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}You should be studying. \NWe've got entrance exams this year.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.11,0:07:41.02,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Are there hot guys? \NDo you have any hot guys?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.65,0:07:44.15,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I want to be able to date.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.15,0:07:46.90,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}I'd be worried about the stares, \Nand it seems dangerous.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.32,Default,Char,0,0,0,,It's creepy, so no.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.07,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Sorry. It's creepy, so no.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.07,0:07:51.41,Default,Char,0,0,0,,It's creepy, so no.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.83,0:07:54.33,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Creepy.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.33,0:07:54.75,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.75,0:07:55.16,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Creepy.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.16,0:07:55.83,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.83,0:07:57.08,Default,Char,0,0,0,,It's creepy, so no.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.88,0:08:04.96,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}It really was impossible to find \Nnew members this time of the year.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.47,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Not to mention we just keep getting called creepy.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.47,0:08:09.47,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Now even I want to quit.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.18,0:08:12.89,Default,Char,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.06,0:08:15.73,Default,Char,0,0,0,,The president's lost it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.73,0:08:17.06,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Please calm down!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.06,0:08:20.65,Default,Char,0,0,0,,The going-home club...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.11,0:08:22.86,Default,Char,0,0,0,,President!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.86,0:08:25.36,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I've brought him! He's not in any clubs or committees,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.36,0:08:27.03,Default,Char,0,0,0,,and he doesn't seem to have a girlfriend or any friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.03,0:08:28.86,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Salt Middle School's final go-homer and all-round bum,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.99,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Kageyama Shigeo of class 2-1.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.99,0:08:32.62,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Well, he's basically right.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.62,0:08:34.45,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Well done, Inukawa!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.45,0:08:36.83,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Let me introduce you \Nto the other members, Kageyama.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.83,0:08:39.04,Default,Char,0,0,0,,This is Kijibayashi, and Saruta.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.04,0:08:39.87,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.87,0:08:40.67,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.67,0:08:44.96,Default,Char,0,0,0,,And I'm the president, Kurata Tome, from class 3-5.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.88,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Call me Tome.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.97,0:08:51.84,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}The president is desperate!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.34,0:08:56.14,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Tome... That's my grandmother's name.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.14,0:08:59.56,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I-I'm sure that's because of fate, too! There you have it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.39,0:09:01.81,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Join the Telepathy Club!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.81,0:09:02.86,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I can't today.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.86,0:09:04.23,Default,Char,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.23,0:09:07.36,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Wait a second, Mob! You actually have plans?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.36,0:09:11.03,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Yeah. After this, I have to go to my exorcism job.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.41,0:09:13.57,Default,Char,0,0,0,,E-Exorcism? What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.57,0:09:18.00,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Ah, President! Actually, this guy \Nwas sort of famous in grade school.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.33,0:09:21.12,Default,Char,0,0,0,,He could bend spoons and make erasers move...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.12,0:09:22.08,Default,Char,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.46,0:09:24.34,Default,Char,0,0,0,,He's an esper!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.34,0:09:27.34,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Stop being weird and just join our club.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.34,0:09:30.09,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I'm sure the exorcism can wait a little while.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.97,0:09:35.85,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Hey, what's up, Mob?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.85,0:09:36.97,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah, Master.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.43,0:09:40.89,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Is it all right if I'm a little late today? \NI'm being recruited into a club.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.89,0:09:42.85,Default,Char,0,0,0,,That should be over instantly.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.85,0:09:45.56,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}No, I actually have to wait \Nuntil the student council meeting is over,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.56,0:09:47.86,Default,Char,0,0,0,,and then go submit my club admission form.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.86,0:09:51.99,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Uh, wait. So if I tell you I need you to \Ncome immediately, you're not going to join?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.99,0:09:56.24,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Yes, well... Shouldn't I keep the promise I made first?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.24,0:09:58.62,Default,Char,0,0,0,,So it's not like you actually want to join?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.62,0:09:59.83,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Not really, no.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.25,0:10:01.71,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Then hurry on over.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.71,0:10:04.29,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Show them how fast someone \Nin the going-home club can leave school.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.63,Default,Char,0,0,0,,He says he needs me right away, so I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.63,0:10:08.96,Default,Char,0,0,0,,P-Put me on for a sec!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.51,0:10:12.80,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}I really need Kageyama \Nto join this club, no matter what!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.22,0:10:16.55,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}A girl, eh? She must be trying to use Mob.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.55,0:10:18.89,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Mob's not the type to play any sports.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.39,0:10:20.72,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Forcing him into things isn't good.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.72,0:10:22.56,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're not a sports club!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.56,0:10:24.10,Default,Char,0,0,0,,We're the Telepathy Club!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.10,0:10:25.56,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Huh? What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.56,0:10:28.32,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}It's a club where we train in order \Nto feel telepathic powers.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.32,0:10:31.49,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Yeah, that sounds shady as hell. \NWhat do you mean by "telepathy"?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.49,0:10:34.03,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Like you're one to talk!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.03,0:10:38.28,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I heard that Kageyama has ESP,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.28,0:10:41.54,Default,Char,0,0,0,,but aren't you using that to get more customers?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.54,0:10:43.33,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Because you're a phony!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.33,0:10:44.96,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth, amateur!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.96,0:10:48.79,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Don't you dare try to steal away my \Ndisciple's precious time with your nonsense!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.79,0:10:49.55,Default,Char,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.05,0:10:53.01,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Are you saying that you don't care \Nif our club gets abolished?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.01,0:10:55.55,Default,Char,0,0,0,,We're going to be kicked out of the room!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.97,0:11:01.27,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Master, Tome is about to cry, \Nso I'm thinking about joining after all...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.27,0:11:02.64,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't be fooled!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.64,0:11:04.02,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those are crocodile tears!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.35,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Bonds, memories, and friendship...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.35,0:11:11.23,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Like any of those things will disappear because a club is abolished.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.48,0:11:15.74,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! They just don't want to lose their room, their budget,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.03,0:11:20.53,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}and their pointless after-school time, \Njudging from what their club sounds like.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.87,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}See through it, Mob!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.29,0:11:26.37,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}That shady club is going down \Nbecause it's meant to go down.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.75,0:11:28.96,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you understand, hurry up and come to work!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.59,0:11:31.55,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I understand...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.38,0:11:35.72,Default,Char,0,0,0,,And so, I'll be leaving after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.43,0:11:39.93,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Wait! Hear me out, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.93,0:11:43.27,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}It seems that the president \Nseriously believes in telepathy,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.77,0:11:46.81,Default,Char,0,0,0,,but honestly, yeah, I just want to goof off.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.81,0:11:49.52,Default,Char,0,0,0,,But right now, we're in middle school.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.52,0:11:52.48,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}This is the only time we're \Ngoing to be able to goof off!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.90,0:11:56.95,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Play cards with us in this lazy \Nlittle paradise we've created!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.74,0:12:00.57,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}You're not going to find \Na more carefree club than this.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.57,0:12:03.83,Default,Char,0,0,0,,We have until tomorrow, so think it over.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.62,0:12:08.75,Default,Char,0,0,0,,You're our last hope, Kageyama!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.46,0:12:12.67,Default,Char,0,0,0,,You properly declined, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.67,0:12:15.34,Default,Char,0,0,0,,No. I thought I'd think about it overnight.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.67,0:12:18.59,Default,Char,0,0,0,,You shouldn't procrastinate, Mob.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.60,Default,Char,0,0,0,,You need to properly decline things that you don't want to do.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.18,0:12:24.22,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Right now, the thing I least want to do
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.73,Default,Char,0,0,0,,is be dressed like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.39,0:12:28.69,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Oh, there it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.69,0:12:30.81,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Saint Highso Girls' Academy.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.81,0:12:32.86,Default,Char,0,0,0,,It's a private all-girls high school.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.23,0:12:36.15,Default,Char,0,0,0,,We're meeting the clients up on the roof.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.15,0:12:36.78,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.99,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Stop! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.99,0:12:39.70,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Pardon?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.70,0:12:42.03,Default,Char,0,0,0,,You! I'm talking to you! Don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.03,0:12:44.33,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I'm a student here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.33,0:12:45.45,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Reporting from the front gate.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.91,Default,Char,0,0,0,,A suspicious individual showed up!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.08,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Requesting backup!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.41,0:12:50.25,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Hey, that's a bit mean, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.25,0:12:51.63,Default,Char,0,0,0,,You perverted weirdo!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.21,0:12:54.17,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew this wouldn't work.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.17,0:12:56.42,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}But thank god that they saw \Nthrough our disguises so early.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.42,0:12:59.01,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't want to infiltrate the school dressed up like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.34,0:13:01.14,Default,Char,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.14,0:13:03.35,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Now hurry up and get away from the pervert.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.35,0:13:04.18,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.10,0:13:07.85,Default,Char,0,0,0,,We'll deal with the suspicious individual.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.73,0:13:12.56,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.24,0:13:27.75,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}Won't I get in trouble if I'm busted?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.29,0:13:32.75,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}He said we were meeting on the roof, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.05,0:13:39.88,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Um, hello.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.17,0:13:43.89,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I've come from the consultation office. Are you the clients?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.89,0:13:45.97,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Huh? Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.97,0:13:48.35,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}I never saw your face before. \NAre you a transfer student?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.35,0:13:48.97,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.97,0:13:50.14,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Consultation office?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.14,0:13:53.10,Default,Char,0,0,0,,You trying to get through to us thugs?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.10,0:13:54.02,Default,Char,0,0,0,,So annoying!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.27,0:13:58.36,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Like we're going to let some twerp like you lecture us!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.36,0:13:59.15,Default,Char,0,0,0,,No, I'm just—
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.15,0:14:02.03,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Why don't you mind your own business?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.03,0:14:04.41,Default,Char,0,0,0,,If you don't, you're going to regret it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.91,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Sorry about that...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.41,0:14:09.58,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Man, talk about a downer. Let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.58,0:14:10.50,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.29,0:14:15.67,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.13,0:14:19.09,Default,Char,0,0,0,,You instantly got picked on by thugs. How funny.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.59,0:14:21.55,Default,Char,0,0,0,,We're your clients.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.97,0:14:25.22,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Isn't that Reigen guy coming?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.22,0:14:27.39,Default,Char,0,0,0,,He was caught at the front gate.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.39,0:14:30.52,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Also, you both came here dressed as girls? Seriously?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.52,0:14:33.60,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}He couldn't get us permission to come in,\Nso we didn't have a choice...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.60,0:14:34.44,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.98,0:14:36.86,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Sorry to make you go through all that.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:36.86,0:14:42.24,Default,Char,0,0,0,,The school just refuses to take us seriously.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.24,0:14:44.61,Default,Char,0,0,0,,What did you tell them?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.61,0:14:47.74,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Students' belongings have \Nmysteriously been disappearing,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.74,0:14:49.49,Default,Char,0,0,0,,and we've been hearing weird noises...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.25,Default,Char,0,0,0,,What do you call it, a poltergeist phenomenon?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.83,0:14:54.75,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}We heard things have been spotted \Nfloating through the air, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.75,0:14:58.54,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Right. Apparently, a bra started floating \Naround on its own in the locker room.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.54,0:15:00.09,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bra...?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.38,0:15:04.26,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}We're dead sure it has to \Nbe something supernatural.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.26,0:15:11.31,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}So we just called the cheapest exorcist in the area \Nand somehow ended up with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.31,0:15:11.97,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.27,0:15:16.31,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}You're a guy, but you were trembling so much\Ndealing with some high school girls.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.98,Default,Char,0,0,0,,You must be quite the reliable gentleman.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.98,0:15:20.15,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.15,0:15:22.44,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}That was sarcasm, duh! \NShe wasn't complimenting you!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.78,0:15:25.32,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Are you sure we can trust you?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.32,0:15:26.49,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I have my doubts.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.49,0:15:27.99,Default,Char,0,0,0,,You seem unreliable.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.12,Default,Char,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.12,0:15:31.24,Default,Char,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.24,0:15:33.25,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I-It's fine...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.75,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I just have to perform an exorcism.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.46,0:15:40.46,Default,Char,0,0,0,,If you feel anything spiritual, let us know.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.59,0:15:42.42,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.88,0:15:46.76,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Well? Do you sense anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.05,0:15:48.64,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Just slightly...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.64,0:15:50.60,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if he's being serious...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.14,0:15:53.72,Default,Char,0,0,0,,It's nearby.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.72,0:15:55.48,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.48,0:15:57.35,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Someone!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.27,0:16:00.77,Default,Char,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.77,0:16:02.69,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Something was here...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.19,0:16:06.07,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Something was looking in from the top of the door...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.28,0:16:09.24,Default,Char,0,0,0,,The windows are locked.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.24,0:16:11.95,Default,Char,0,0,0,,And no one's gone through the exit.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.58,0:16:14.58,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I'm going to find the spirit.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.58,0:16:20.21,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Nothing so far?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.63,0:16:22.92,Default,Char,0,0,0,,We can trust you, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.92,0:16:24.05,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.26,Default,Char,0,0,0,,You still can't find it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.93,0:16:29.43,Default,Char,0,0,0,,The spirit's angry.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.43,0:16:30.30,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.97,0:16:34.14,Default,Char,0,0,0,,If we keep pursuing it, it might try to do something.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.14,0:16:35.97,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Eek! What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.97,0:16:38.31,Default,Char,0,0,0,,The basketball team is practicing inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.85,0:16:40.40,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I'm going to end this.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.65,0:16:45.15,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I've trapped the spirit.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.91,0:16:54.08,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Pass! Pass! Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.12,0:16:56.83,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I've found you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.83,0:17:00.08,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.88,0:17:04.75,Default,Char,0,0,0,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.75,0:17:07.01,Default,Char,0,0,0,,What is that?! A ghost?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.51,0:17:10.51,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Psychic brat...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.51,0:17:14.30,Default,Char,0,0,0,,How dare you trap me?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.30,0:17:16.77,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Are you going to try to ruin my paradise?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.89,0:17:20.31,Default,Char,0,0,0,,This is what you'll get!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.53,0:17:34.28,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crap. I underestimated the psychic.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.28,0:17:37.62,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't take a hostage, he'll erase me!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.91,0:17:42.29,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}You smell nice.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.29,0:17:44.04,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I choose you!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.09,0:17:46.00,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.80,0:17:47.50,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.03,0:18:10.32,Default,Char,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.32,0:18:11.49,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.49,0:18:13.32,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\a6}Want to go home together today?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.53,0:18:11.99,Alt,Char,0,0,0,,How did you do that?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.65,Alt,Char,0,0,0,,{\a6}What class is she in?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.49,0:18:13.32,Default,Char,0,0,0,,So cool!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.99,0:18:13.32,Alt,Char,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.32,0:18:16.20,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Listen to them cheer. Good for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.20,0:18:18.83,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}Thanks. Apparently you \Nwere pretty reliable after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.41,0:18:21.37,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.37,0:18:25.71,Default,Char,0,0,0,,To think that I was defeated by a loser like you...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.71,0:18:29.38,Default,Char,0,0,0,,And I thought I'd finally be happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.76,0:18:33.09,Default,Char,0,0,0,,You and I are the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.09,0:18:34.13,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Same?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.68,0:18:38.06,Default,Char,0,0,0,,The way you get nervous around girls...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.06,0:18:41.64,Default,Char,0,0,0,,You're playing the loser role just like me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.77,0:18:43.64,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Things...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.06,0:18:47.98,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Things finally started to get fun for me after my death.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.98,0:18:50.28,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I was fulfilled.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.28,0:18:53.20,Default,Char,0,0,0,,But I guess it's all over now.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.49,0:18:59.91,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Hey... Are you living your every day to the fullest?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.21,Default,Char,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.67,0:19:14.72,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}You seem out of it. \NIs something bothering you?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.72,0:19:17.26,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Huh? No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.30,Default,Char,0,0,0,,All right, then...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.14,0:19:24.60,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Mob!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.60,0:19:26.44,Default,Char,0,0,0,,You came!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.44,0:19:28.90,Default,Char,0,0,0,,We believed in you, Kageyama!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.23,0:19:31.94,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Now, hurry up and sign this club admission form.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.69,0:19:37.16,Default,Char,0,0,0,,You're already here? That was awfully quick...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.53,0:19:38.66,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Vice President!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.66,0:19:42.37,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Well, I had to show this room...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.66,0:19:44.04,Default,Char,0,0,0,,to them.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.37,0:19:50.46,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}This room will become the club room \Nfor the newly formed Body Improvement Club.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.34,Default,Char,0,0,0,,What?! Hey, hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.80,0:19:54.67,Default,Char,0,0,0,,The Telepathy Club won't be abolished!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.67,0:19:57.55,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Kageyama here is just about to join!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.55,0:19:58.59,Default,Char,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.89,0:20:00.51,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Are you insane?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.51,0:20:01.60,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.60,0:20:03.47,Default,Char,0,0,0,,What grade are you in?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.47,0:20:04.22,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I'm a second-year.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.22,0:20:06.60,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Do you have any experience in other clubs?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.60,0:20:07.35,Default,Char,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.35,0:20:10.23,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Do you have a close friend in the Telepathy Club?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.23,0:20:11.48,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I have an acquaintance.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.48,0:20:12.36,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Do you go to cram school?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.36,0:20:13.36,Default,Char,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.36,0:20:14.23,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Do you study?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.23,0:20:15.36,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.36,0:20:16.36,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Do you have any hobbies?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.36,0:20:16.99,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.99,0:20:19.11,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Don't you have anything that you want to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.91,0:20:20.62,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.24,0:20:25.12,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}If you let them drive you into joining\Ndespite having no interest in the club at all,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.12,0:20:27.00,Default,Char,0,0,0,,what exactly will you gain from it?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.25,0:20:30.75,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Well, I just want to live my every day to the fullest.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.75,0:20:36.01,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}And will spending your time after school with cola, \Nsnacks, and video games help you do that?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.01,0:20:39.55,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}If you want to join of your own \Nfree will, I will not stop you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.55,0:20:41.68,Default,Char,0,0,0,,However, you should carefully reconsider this.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.43,0:20:45.27,Default,Char,0,0,0,,What is it that you really want to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.89,0:20:47.27,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(0,181)}What I want to do...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.06,0:20:49.98,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(0,310)}Do I have anything I want to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.77,0:20:52.40,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(0,222)}Does everyone else have something?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.36,0:20:56.74,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}Something enjoyable?\NSomething I'm envious of?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.74,0:20:58.70,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are they enjoying?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.70,0:21:01.70,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}Clubs, hobbies, and studying?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.24,0:21:05.20,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hanging out with girls might be fun...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.58,0:21:08.54,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}I did have a dream!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.54,0:21:11.46,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}I wanted to confess my feelings \Nto my first love, Tsubomi,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.46,0:21:14.13,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}and walk home together, holding hands.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.55,0:21:18.30,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Look, Tsubomi.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.67,0:21:20.84,Default,Char,0,0,0,,When you make frogs float, they start swimming.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.84,0:21:23.47,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Wow, how cute.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.47,0:21:26.39,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I can make the bar all squishy.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.39,0:21:27.89,Default,Char,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Mob.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.31,0:21:32.65,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Look! I'm only showing you, Tsubomi!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.90,0:21:35.23,Default,Char,0,0,0,,That's boring.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.94,0:21:39.65,Default,Char,0,0,0,,The red team is fast!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.45,0:21:45.20,Default,Char,0,0,0,,You're so fast, Akira!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.74,0:21:49.75,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right. If I can change anything by joining a club...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.92,0:21:53.67,Default,Char,0,0,0,,I'll join!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.04,0:21:56.50,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Thank you for having me,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.84,0:21:58.67,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Body Improvement Club!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.71,0:22:01.01,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Huh? You want to join us?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.59,0:22:03.26,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.84,0:22:05.76,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Sure! Let's work hard together!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.76,0:22:06.68,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.03,0:23:43.19,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unable to locate the whereabouts
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:46.86,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1\q2}of the suspicious individual who tried \Nto infiltrate an all-girls school
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.86,0:23:48.32,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}in broad daylight by crossdressing,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.32,0:23:49.87,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\i1}the whole area is on high alert...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.58,0:23:54.95,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.58,0:23:57.42,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Mob successfully joins the Body Improvement Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.42,0:23:59.54,Default,Char,0,0,0,,On his way home, in an attempt to be popular,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.54,0:24:02.00,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}he heads to the main temple \Nof an obviously shady-looking cult.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:03.51,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Are you really sure about this, Mob?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.51,0:24:05.26,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Next time on Mob Psycho 100 Episode 3:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.26,0:24:07.47,Default,Char,0,0,0,,{\q2}"An Invite to a Meeting\N~Simply Put, I Just Want to be Popular~"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.47,0:24:09.97,Default,Char,0,0,0,,Recording it? That's also a wise decision.
